# Unit 1: Encoding Numbers in the Real World

## Background

Today's news &mdash; as well as history &mdash; is rich with fascinating stories about encoding numbers in computers. Some stories vividly illustrate the problems that can arise.

## Lesson

* Examine real-world issues related to number encoding in computers
* Share your knowledge with your class through a jigsaw activity.

